<h1>Team Fox Summer Series - Gift Your Birthday</h1>
<p><img src="/files/AbbeyTutterow360.jpg" style="float: left; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid #ccc; margin: 0 20px 20px 0;" />Looking for a fun way to make your summer birthday extra memorable? Why not throw a bash on behalf of Team Fox and challenge your friends and family to support a great cause while celebrating your special day? Check out some of our tips and tricks below to get started!</p>
<h2 style="clear: both;">Instructions</h2>
<ol>
<li><span>1.</span>
<p><strong>Register:</strong> <a href="https://secure3.convio.net/mjff/site/TRR/TeamFox/TeamFox/1366814297?pg=utype&amp;fr_id=1890" class="orange">Register online</a> as a Team Fox member and create a personalized fundraising page to share your event details and collect donations. Once you register your event, we’ll send you a detailed step-by-step toolkit with an event checklist and helpful materials.</p>
</li>
<li><span>2.</span>
<p><strong>Start planning:</strong> Pick a date and figure out what supplies you’ll need. If you’re asking for guests to make a donation in lieu of gifts, think about some fun ways to thank them for their support.</p>
</li>
<li><span>3.</span>
<p><strong>Get creative:</strong> There are lots of ways to bring the fun to your party. Consider throwing a pizza or pool party, including an ice cream sundae bar or giving the whole party a theme with costumes and prizes.</p>
</li>
<li><span>4.</span>
<p><strong>Invite your friends:</strong> Invite your closest buds to attend and remind friends and family from afar to support your efforts by donating to your Team Fox fundraising page!</p>
</li>
<li><span>5.</span>
<p><strong>Enjoy some cake:</strong> Seriously, you’ve earned it! Celebrate your big day knowing that you’ve helped Team Fox get one step closer to finding a cure for Parkinson’s.</p>
</li>
<li><span>6.</span>
<p><strong>Share your success:</strong> Held an awesome event? We want to hear about it! Be sure to write up a quick recap and send us some photos to be entered to win a Team Fox Summer Prize Pack! On social media? <a href="https://www.facebook.com/teamfox" class="orange">Friend us on Facebook</a> and share your updates on Twitter using the hashtag: #TeamFoxSummer</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p>Don't have enough time to get a party together, but still want to use your birthday for good? No problem! Consider gifting your birthday to Team Fox by setting up a fundraising page and asking friends and family to make a donation in lieu of gifts.</p>
<p>Have a question? We’re here to help! Email us at <a href="mailto:teamfox@michaeljfox.org" class="orange">teamfox@michaeljfox.org.</a></p>
<p class="pad20t"><a href="https://secure3.convio.net/mjff/site/TRR/TeamFox/TeamFox/1366814297?pg=utype&amp;fr_id=1890" class="mjffButton">     Get Started     </a></p>
<h2 class="pad30t">Looking for some inspiration?</h2>
<p><a href="#"><img src="/images/abby360.jpg" alt="Abby" style="float: right; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid #CCC; margin: 0 0 20px 20px;" /></a>Instead of your traditional birthday party, Abby had a Pancakes for Parkinson’s birthday party and she raised $2,000! You can create your own unique birthday party just like Abby! Consider a pool, pizza or pancake party for your birthday-they all begin with P’s too!</p>
